translation[10]{c,v,t}:
  30,51,Aur agar hum ek aisi hawa bhej dein jiske asar se woh apni kheti ko zard paayein to woh kufr karte reh jaate hain
  30,52,"(Aey Nabi) Tum murdon ko nahin suna sakte, na unn behron ko apni pukar suna sakte ho jo peeth pherey bhaagay chaley jaa rahe hon"
  30,53,"Aur na tum andhon ko unki gumrahi se nikaal kar raah e raast dikha sakte ho, tum to sirf unhi ko suna sakte ho jo hamari aayat par iman latey aur sar-e-tasleem kham kar detey hain"
  30,54,"Allah hi to hai jisne zoaf (kamzori) ki haalat mein tumhari paidaish ki ibtida ki, phir is zoaf (kamzori) ke baad tumhein quwwat bakshi, phir is quwwat ke baad tumhein zaeef aur buda (old) kardiya. Woh jo kuch chahta hai paida karta hai, aur woh sabkuch janne wala, har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai"
  30,55,Aur jab woh sa-aat (hour) barpa hogi to mujrim kasmein kha kha kar kahenge ke hum ek ghadi bhar se zyada nahin thehre hain.Isi taraah woh duniya ki zindagi mein dhoka khaya karte thay
  30,56,"Magar jo ilm aur iman se behramand (endowed) kiye gaye thay woh kahenge ke khuda ke nawishte (record) mein to tum roz-e-hashar tak paday rahey ho. So yeh wahi roz-e-hashar hai, lekin tum jante na thay"
  30,57,Pas woh din hoga jismein zaalimon ko unki maazrat koi nafa (faida) na degi aur na unsey maafi maangne ke liye kaha jayega
  30,58,"Humne is Quran mein logon ko tarah tarah se samjhaya hai, tum khwah koi nishani le aao, jin logon ne maanne se inkar kardiya hai wo yahi kahenge ke tum baatil(falsehood) par ho"
  30,59,Is tarah thappa (seal) laga deta hai Allah un logon ke dilon par jo be-ilm hain
  30,60,"Pas (Aey Nabi) sabr karo, yaqeenan Allah ka wada sachha hai. Aur hargiz halka na payein tumko woh log jo yaqeen nahin laatey"